	"system": {
		"description": "<p>When you choose this archetype at 3rd level, you gain the following Channel Divinity options:</p><h2>Joke of the Century</h2><p>As an action, you unleash a sudden barrage of divine foolishness—prismatic flashes, booming jokes, illusory balloons, or magical slapstick.</p><p>Choose a number of creatures equal to your Charisma modifier within 30 feet. Each must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be [[/condition id=confused]] until the end of your next turn. If they fail the saving throw by 5 or more, they are [[/condition id=incapacitated]] until the end of your next turn as they can’t stop laughing.</p><h2>Burst of Joy</h2><p>As a bonus action, you release an aura of uplifting radiance. You and all allies within 30 ft are cured of the [[/condition id=frightened]] condition and have advantage on the next saving throw you make for 1 minute.</p><p></p>",
